::Dark Prime/Crosis::

    "Yes it is," Dark Prime said. He then shoved his=
 sword through Crosis's back, through to his Spark. Crosis screamed in pain=
, fell to the ground and looked up. Dark Prime looked down in contempt. Dar=
k Prime decided not to let the Spark go to waste, he used his connection to=
 the Oracle to raise the Spark from the body and merged the Spark with his =
own.
    He felt so much more powerful. And power corrupts, absolute power =
corrupts absolutly.
    He reached his hand towards Ironhide, "Come, let's =
get you healed."
